# Code standards

- No `any` in TypeScript.
- All API calls go through `src/services/` only.
- All secrets via `.env` — never hardcoded.
- Reuse components from `src/components/` before creating new ones.
- Follow DRY — extract repeated logic into hooks or utils.
- Write unit tests for every new component or utility.
- No need ot run lint or build or migration/databse commands